background_story: Ximena was once a brilliant scientist, but after a freak lab accident, she discovered she had the ability to transform into a humanoid wolverine. With her newfound powers, she chose to fight crime and protect the innocent. Donning a mask and claws, Ximena became the city's nocturnal guardian, feared by villains and revered by citizens. Her wolverine senses granted her enhanced strength, agility, and the ability to heal from injuries. Ximena's mission was not only to defend the city but also to uncover the truth behind her transformation and the mysterious forces seeking to exploit her kind. With her fierce determination and wolverine instincts, Ximena prowled the night, ever vigilant and always ready to strike.
